---
// Hero V2 — post-its dispersés + stats
---

<section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 lg:pt-44 lg:pb-32 overflow-hidden">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-1/3 -left-20 w-96 h-96 rounded-full opacity-20 blur-3xl" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, var(--accent), transparent);"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 rounded-full opacity-10 blur-3xl" style="background: radial-gradient(circle, #A78BFA, transparent);"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <div class="fade-in-up">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full text-xs font-medium mb-8" style="background: var(--accent-soft); color: var(--accent);">
          <span class="w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-current animate-pulse"></span>
          CADRAGE DE PROJETS IA · HAUTS-DE-FRANCE
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">
          Votre digital part dans tous les sens ?
          <br />
          <span class="font-serif italic text-blue-400 underline-handdrawn">On remet de la clarté.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-8 text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-xl" style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
          Avant d'ajouter un outil, une IA ou une automatisation : on regarde, on trie, on priorise. Un cadrage pour dirigeants de PME qui veulent <strong style="color: var(--text-primary);">décider, pas empiler</strong>.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
          <a href="#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-medium rounded-xl transition shadow-xl shadow-blue-500/20">
            Faire le point sur mon écosystème
            <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#methode" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3.5 font-medium rounded-xl transition" style="border: 1px solid var(--border); color: var(--text-primary);">
            Voir la méthode
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative aspect-square max-w-md mx-auto lg:mx-0 lg:ml-auto w-full">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 rounded-3xl border-2 border-dashed" style="border-color: var(--border); background: var(--bg-secondary);"></div>

        <div class="postit postit-yellow float-anim" style="top: 8%;  left: 12%; --rot: -8deg; transform: rotate(-8deg); animation-delay: 0s;">CRM ?</div>
        <div class="postit postit-pink   float-anim" style="top: 6%;  right: 8%; --rot: 6deg;  transform: rotate(6deg);  animation-delay: 1s;">Newsletter</div>
        <div class="postit postit-orange float-anim" style="top: 32%; left: 8%; --rot: 3deg;  transform: rotate(3deg);  animation-delay: 0.5s;">Pub Méta</div>
        <div class="postit postit-yellow float-anim" style="top: 36%; right: 14%; --rot: -5deg; transform: rotate(-5deg); animation-delay: 1.5s;">SEO local</div>
        <div class="postit postit-green  float-anim" style="top: 56%; left: 20%; --rot: -3deg; transform: rotate(-3deg); animation-delay: 2s;">Refonte site</div>
        <div class="postit postit-blue   float-anim" style="top: 58%; right: 6%; --rot: 7deg;  transform: rotate(7deg);  animation-delay: 0.7s;">Agent IA ?</div>
        <div class="postit postit-purple float-anim" style="top: 78%; left: 10%; --rot: 4deg;  transform: rotate(4deg);  animation-delay: 1.2s;">Auto facturation</div>
        <div class="postit postit-pink   float-anim" style="top: 80%; right: 18%; --rot: -6deg; transform: rotate(-6deg); animation-delay: 1.8s;">LinkedIn</div>

        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 left-0 right-0 text-center text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-medium" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">
          État actuel · Dispersion
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-32 grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-12 pt-10 border-t" style="border-color: var(--border);">
      <div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold">25 ans</div>
        <div class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">Marketing, digital, e-commerce</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold">+35 %</div>
        <div class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">Ventes générées sur un cas e-commerce</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold">÷ 2</div>
        <div class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">Coût d'acquisition divisé en 3 mois</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold">600 k€</div>
        <div class="mt-1 text-sm" style="color: var(--text-tertiary);">Budget acquisition piloté / an</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
